Next Generation Sequencing (NGS) Market - Competitive and Segmentation Analysis:

**Segments**

- On the basis of product & services, the Next Generation Sequencing (NGS) market can be segmented into reagents & consumables, sequencing services, instruments, and software.
- By technology, the market can be divided into sequencing by synthesis, ion semiconductor sequencing, single-molecule realtime (SMRT) sequencing, nanopore sequencing, and others.
- When it comes to application, the NGS market encompasses segments such as diagnostics, drug discovery, agricultural & animal research, and others.
- Based on end-users, the market is categorized into academic research institutes, pharmaceutical & biotechnology companies, hospitals & clinics, and others.

